'''BlackBerry Playbook OS'''是基于[[QNX|QNX Neutrino]] [[实时操作系统|实时操作系统]]的新型操作系统，据报道可以运行为[[Google|Google]]的[[Android|Android]]系统开发的应用程序。<ref>http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/133424.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/133424.htm |date=20110130044653 }} 传黑莓平板Playbook将可运行Android应用</ref> <ref>http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-10/rim-is-said-to-plan-playbook-tablet-software-to-run-google-s-android-apps.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-10/rim-is-said-to-plan-playbook-tablet-software-to-run-google-s-android-apps.html |date=20110214145825 }} RIM Said to Plan PlayBook Software to Run Google Apps</ref> 第一款运行此系统的设备将是[[BlackBerry_PlayBook|BlackBerry PlayBook]][[平板电脑|平板电脑]]。<ref name="playbook_pressrelease">[http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/RIM-Unveils-The-BlackBerry-PlayBook-NASDAQ-RIMM-1325727.htm RIM Unveils The BlackBerry PlayBook] {{Wayback|url=http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/RIM-Unveils-The-BlackBerry-PlayBook-NASDAQ-RIMM-1325727.htm |date=20190404044052 }}, official press release, September 27, 2010</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ce.cn/yd/gd/201207/26/t20120726_23525612.shtml |title=黑莓PlayBook OS 2.1泄露 更新十余项功能_中国经济网——国家经济门户 |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230001720/http://www.ce.cn/yd/gd/201207/26/t20120726_23525612.shtml }}</ref>

微內核設計用於分佈式處理，与[[整塊性核心|整块性核心]]架构如Linux相比，減少了散熱和能源使用。鎖定軟件任務到指定核心，由操作系統的單一副本控制，讓所有的資源動態分配并在應用程序之間共享。在應用程序的初始化时，由系統設計者決定的設定強制指定应用的所有线程僅运行在指定的核心，從而降低了處理器間通信開銷并保持總線整洁。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eetimes.com/design/embedded/4006625/Making-the-Most-of-Multi-Core-Processors-Part-1 |title=Making the Most of Multi-Core Processors: Part 1 |accessdate=2013-11-28 |archive-date=2012-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723010523/http://www.eetimes.com/design/embedded/4006625/Making-the-Most-of-Multi-Core-Processors-Part-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>這種方法介于對稱多處理和非對稱多處理之間。

